The paper focuses on evaluating the robustness of image models, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The study also involves examining the performance of different model architectures, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The authors also investigate training techniques to improve model robustness, which is related to neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the study involves analyzing videos, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
